text: 😭 Actually there’s a video from another news channel that explains why this is a really bad thing. There is very little natural forest left in Thailand, not enough for so many elephants. Most of these “tourist parks” allow them to feed and care for the elephant including frequent vet visits. Closure of the parks means that instead of returning to the forests, the elephants may be taken to the city to perform and hope to make money there - which is very dangerous for their welfare and stresses them out
